 value. The data show the VHE emission\noriginating in the entrance and exit of a superluminal knot in and out a\nrecollimation shock in the inner jet. A shock-shock interaction in the jet\nseems responsible for the observed flares and EVPA swing. This scenario is also\nconsistent with the SED modelling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Jul 2018 22:52:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-29"}
