obal phase-coherent state with zero resistance can be formed in such\narrays. Our Monte Carlo results are in very good agreement with experimental\ndata from various types of superconducting nanowire arrays\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Jul 2018 12:02:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-26"}
